  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink15-kilavi">cēṇiṭaip pirintuvantu uṭaṉ uṟaikiṉṟa talaimakaṟkup puṟattoḻukkam
          uḷatākiṉṟatu eṉṟu kuṟippiṉāṉ uṇarntu talaimakaḷ vēṟupaṭṭāḷākat tōḻi ataṉaiyaṟiyātu, ‘avaṉ
          uṭaṉuṟaiyavum vēṟupaṭukiṉṟatu eṉṉai?’ eṉṟāṭku avaḷ colliyatu.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="Aink15">
          <l> maṇalāṭu malirniṟai virumpiya voṇṭaḻaip</l>
          <l> puṉalāṭu makaḷirkkup puṇartuṇai yutavum</l>
          <l> vēḻa mūtū rūra</l>
          <l> ṉūra ṉāyiṉu mūraṉal laṉṉē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:lang="en">
          <l> The man from the town, the old town with wild cane,</l>
          <l rend="indent2"> who helps [his] consort united with the women bathing in the flood</l>
          <l rend="indent2"> [all wearing] bright foliage, they who'd desired the fullness of the
            flood dancing in the sand,</l>
          <l> Even though he is a man from the town, he is not a man of the town.</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
  </text>
